nodes.text: Grayda Paro was a Force-sensitive Zabrak female. Following the Battle of Asylum she traveled to Odessen and joined the Alliance against the Eternal Empire of Zakuul. She was assigned to the Force Enclave branch of the Alliance under Sana-Rae.
Grayda Paro appears in Star Wars: The Old Republic: Knights of the Fallen Empire expansion as a Jedi Knight vendor inside Odessen base.
